Types

VertexDataKind = enum
  VNull, VString, VBool, VFloat, VInt, VObject, VArray
enum object for holding vertex data 
VertexData = ref VertexDataObj
VertexDataObj {...}{.acyclic.} = object
  case kind*: VertexDataKind
  of VString:
      str*: string

  of VInt:
      num*: BiggestInt

  of VBool:
      bval*: bool

  of VFloat:
      fnum*: float

  of VNull:
      nil

  of VObject:
      fields*: OrderedTable[string, VertexData]

  of VArray:
      elems*: seq[VertexData]
